quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20worry%3B%20humans%20receive%20upscale%20services%20as%20well.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dog%20on%20flight%20looking%20out%20window%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66159a861caec1275a6e47fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20capable%20of%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20seats%20can't%20lie%20flat%20due%20to%20the%20plane's%20layout.%3Cp%3EBark%20Air%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20lieu%20of%20in-flight%20meal%20service%2C%20Meeker%20said%20a%20chef%20will%20be%20stationed%20at%20the%20terminals%20to%20cook%20pre-flight%20%26quot%3Bcustom%20meals%26quot%3B%20for%20humans.%20Passengers%20would%20also%20have%20the%20option%20to%20order%20complimentary%20mid-flight%20drinks%20and%20snacks%20while%20they%20luxuriate%20in%20the%20aircraft's%20wide%20leather%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20they've%20landed%2C%20the%20humans%20and%20their%20furry%20companions%20can%20take%20a%20complimentary%20car%20service%20to%20their%20destination%20within%20a%2030-mile%20radius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDespite%20all%20these%20amenities%2C%20%2412%2C000%20for%20a%20roundtrip%20New%20York%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20flight%20is%20objectively%20steep%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Meeker%20knows%20it.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20button%20that%20says%20belly%20rubs%20on%20a%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66159a9f3f923f7dab060919%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeeker%20said%20Bark%20Air%20could%20operate%20%26quot%3Bone-off%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bseasonal%26quot%3B%20flights%3Cp%3EBark%20Air%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBark%20Air's%20first%20flight%20is%20scheduled%20to%20depart%20on%20May%2023.%20The%20cheapest%20one-way%20business%20class%20fare%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20on%20the%20same%20day%20is%20currently%20%24623%20with%20Alaska.%20Bringing%20a%20pet%20would%20add%20another%20%24100%20to%20%24150.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHopefully%2C%20this%20is%20the%20highest%20price%20we%20ever%20charge%2C%20but%20that's%20where%20we%20need%20to%20start%2C%26quot%3B%20Bark's%20CEO%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20besides%20the%20goal%20of%20dropping%20fares%2C%20Meeker%20said%20the%20new%20air%20carrier%20could%20expand%20its%20fleet%20or%20add%20more%20routes%2C%20tossing%20around%20options%20like%20Miami%20to%20New%20York%20or%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20transporting%20a%20dog%20across%20the%20country%20or%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%2C%20the%20alternative%20options%20%E2%80%98are%20pretty%20poor%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20CEO%20of%20Bark%20said.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22window%20of%20a%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66159b051caec1275a6e4906%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeeker%20said%20Bark%20Air%20has%20done%20two%20test%20flights%20between%20New%20York%20and%20Florida.%3Cp%3EBark%20Air%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20the%20airline%20and%20the%20pets'%20sizes%2C%20dogs%20on%20commercial%20US%20flights%20must%20be%20kept%20in%20under-seat%20crates%20or%20checked%20in%20the%20plane's%20cargo%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20New%20York%20and%20London%2C%20the%20options%20are%20even%20slimmer%3A%20UK%20law%20requires%20commercial%20airlines%20to%20check%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-your-pets-are-transported-on-commercial-airlines-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanimals%20into%20the%20cargo%20hold%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20flying%20into%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20doing%20so%20can%20be%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdog-dies-in-cargo-hold-of-air-france-flight-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrifying%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20frightening%2C%26quot%3B%20Meeker%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BFor%20people%20who%20consider%20their%20dogs%20part%20of%20the%20family%2C%20the%20cargo%20hold%20is%20something%20they%20would%20never%20do%2C%20or%20they%20would%20do%20it%20as%20the%20absolute%20last%20resort%20out%20of%20desperation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20Meeker%20said%20BarkAir%20would%20be%20operating%20as%20a%20private%20charter%2C%20which%20means%20it%20would%20skirt%20around%20the%20UK's%20restrictions.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20people%20and%20a%20dog%20next%20to%20a%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66159af21caec1275a6e48c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeeker%2C%20left%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20started%20chalking%20out%20Bark%20Air%201%20%C2%BD%20years%20ago%20with%20help%20from%20James%20O'Leary%2C%20chief%20supply%20chain%20officer%20of%20Bark%20who%20previously%20worked%20with%20Amazon%20Air.%3Cp%3EBark%20Air%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETravelers%20can%20also%20join%20crowd-sourced%20private%20charter%20flights%20for%20pets%2C%20although%20these%20often%20come%20at%20a%20steeper%20cost%20than%20Bark%20Air's%20fares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBark%20Air's%20business%20model%20is%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-semi-private-carrier-jsx-burbank-to-phoenix-flight-review-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esemi-private%20air%20carrier%20JSX%2C%20which%20uses%20a%20less%20crowded%20airport%20terminal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%2030-seater%20regional%20airliner%20to%20create%20a%20private-like%20experience.%20Fares%20are%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20screening%20is%20minimal%2C%20and%20passengers%20must%20only%20arrive%2020%20mi