%3Efavorite%20of%20the%20superrich.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20part%20of%20the%20appeal%20for%20the%20ultra-high-net-worthers%20is%20that%20the%20tournament%20is%20held%20at%20Augusta's%20National%20Golf%20Club.%20While%20the%20list%20of%20its%20300%20or%20so%20members%20is%20top%20secret%2C%20several%20billionaires%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20Dirk%20Ziff%2C%20and%20Stanley%20Druckenmiller%20%E2%80%94%20belong%20to%20the%20club%2C%20according%20to%20a%202015%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fgraphics%2F2015-augusta-national-golf-club-members%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20getting%20in%20is%20hard.%20Membership%20is%20by%20invitation%20and%20capped%2C%20meaning%20people%20can%20only%20join%20when%20an%20existing%20member%20leaves%20or%20dies.%20It%20all%20adds%20to%20the%20cachet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20gotten%20to%20a%20point%20where%20they%20almost%20like%20refusing%20people%20because%20it%20makes%20them%20look%2C%20you%20know%2C%20that%20much%20more%20exclusive%2C%26quot%3B%20Barnabas%20Carrega%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20luxury%20travel%20and%20planning%20firm%20GR8%20Experience%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20over%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20whether%20you%20can%20afford%20a%20membership%20or%20not.%20Most%20members%20have%20inherited%20their%20membership%20through%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20Carrega%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Condoleezza%20Rice%20and%20other%20members%20of%20Augusta%20National.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643436205a15060019d8b0d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221609%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Condoleezza%20Rice%20became%20one%20of%20the%20first%20women%20to%20join%20Augusta%20National%20in%202012.%3Cp%3ETimothy%20A.%20Clary%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20%3Cem%3Eare%3C%2Fem%3E%20now%20allowed%20to%20join%20%E2%80%94%20but%20weren't%20admitted%20before%202012.%20One%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faugusta-national-women-memvbers-2012-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20women%20admitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20Darla%20Dee%20Moore%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20the%20late%20billionaire%20Richard%20Rainwater.%20Former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Condoleezza%20Rice%20has%20also%20joined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20basically%20impossible%20to%20play%20there%20if%20you're%20not%20a%20member%2C%26quot%3B%20Carrega%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20who%20you%20are%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20be%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20But%20if%20you're%20not%20a%20member%2C%20you're%20not%20invited%20by%20a%20member%2C%20you're%20not%20getting%20on%20Augusta%20National.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20the%20closest%20most%20golf%20fans%20will%20get%20to%20the%20pristine%20greens%20is%20watching%20the%20Masters%20on%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAugusta%20National's%20famous%20jackets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20exclusive%20clubs%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0literal%20or%20metaphorical%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20status%20symbols%20involved%20with%20membership%2C%20specifically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-green-jacket-rules-jon-rahm-tiger-woods%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAugusta%20National's%20coveted%20green%20jackets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Only%20members%20and%20Masters%20winners%20can%20wear%20them%2C%20and%20they%20must%20be%20kept%20on%20the%20premises%20(though%20winners%20can%20take%20them%20home%20and%20sport%20them%20at%20approved%20events%20for%2012%20months%20before%20they%20must%20return%20them%20to%20the%20club's%20grounds.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20regulations%2C%20the%20sports%20coat%20is%20considered%20the%20most%20prestigious%20trophy%20in%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20care%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Billy%20Casper%2C%20the%20champion%20of%20the%201970%20tournament%2C%20once%20said%20when%20asked%20how%20much%20money%20he%20would%20take%20home%20from%20the%20tournament.%20%26quot%3BThe%20green%20coat%20is%20enough%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20item%20is%20worth%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20In%202013%2C%20before%20Augusta%20enacted%20strict%20rules%20around%20selling%20the%20blazers%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-green-jacket-cheap-mystery-impossible-buy-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreen%20jacket%20belonging%20to%20Horton%20Smith%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20tournament's%201934%20winner%2C%20was%20auctioned%20off%20for%20%24682%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225460%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Augusta%20National%20member%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6615a0381caec1275a6e4caf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20names%20of%20Augusta%20National%20members%20are%20kept%20confidential%2C%20though%20their%20green%20jackets%20are%20a%20tell.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Squire%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrivate%20jets%20and%20patron%20badges%3A%20How%20billionaires%20attend%20the%20Masters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20gain%20a%20spot%20on%20the%20club's%20exclusive%20roster%2C%20plenty%20of%20billionaires%20who%20aren't%20known%20members%20of%20Augusta%20National%20do%20attend%20the%20Masters%20Tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-masters-chaos-augusta-regional-airport-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20private%20aircraft%20landed%20at%20Augusta%20Regional%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20nearby%20hubs%2C%20according%20to%20information%20from%20the%20aircraft-tracking%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjetspy.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJetSpy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jet%20of%20Phil%20Knight%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20Nike%20CEO%20who's%20worth%20%2438%20billion%20and%20who%20is%20a%20frequent%20attendee%20%E2%80%94%20was%20among%20the%20pack%2C%20according%20to%20the%20JetSpy%20data.%20Planes%20belonging%20to%20other%20billionaires%2C%20including%20hotelier%20Robert%20Rowling%2C%20investor%20Herbert%20Allen%20Jr.%2C%20software%20titan%20David%20Duffield%2C%20Carvana%20founder%20Ernest%20Garcia%2C%20and%20private%20equity%20investor%20Greg%20Mondre%2C%20also%20touched%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelebrities%20like%20Garth%20Brooks%20and%20Luke%20Bryan%2C%20as%20well%20as%20top%20golfers%20like%20Rory%20McIlroy%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiger-woods-ends-nike-partnership-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiger%20Woods%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20billionaire%20in%20his%20own%20right)%2C%20registered%20planes%20that%20landed%20nearby%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20a%20ticket%2C%20though%2C%20is%20not%20simple.%20The%20club%20conducts%20a%20lottery%20for%20tickets%20each%20year%3B%20last%20year%2C%20one-day%20passes%20went%20for%20%24140%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20relatively%20cheap%20by%20many%20people's%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-tickets-lottery%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epatron%20badges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%2C%20like%20nearly%20everything%20else%20at%20Augusta%2C%20are%20veiled%20in%20secrecy.%20No%20one%20outside%20the%20club%20knows%20how%20many%20exist%2C%20but%20once%20you%20are%20offered%20one%2C%20you%20can%20access%20tickets%20for%20life.%20(Patrons%20still%20have%20to%20pay%20annually%20to%20attend%3B%20last%20year%2C%20a%20four-day%20pass%20cost%20%24450.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20with%20everything%20at%20Augusta%20National%2C%20there%20are%20strict%20rules%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fhow-to-get-us-masters-tickets-tournament-schedule%23how-to-buy-tickets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereselling%20Masters%20tickets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Still%2C%20sites%20like%20StubHub%20and%20Ticketmaster%20have%20a%20handful%20of%20four-day%20passes%20available%20for%20upwards%20of%20%2410%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFinding%20a%20place%20to%20sleep%20can%20be%20tough%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0no%20matter%20who%20you%20are%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-tournament-augusta-georgia-house-rentals-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebillionaires%20rent%20local%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%2C%20there%20aren't%20all%20that%20many%20options%20available.%20Most%20hotels%20sell%20out%20of%20rooms%20far%20before%20the%20tournament%20or%20charge%20many%20times%20the%20typical%20nightly%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fairness%2C%20that's%20not%20restricted%20to%20this%20tournament.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgolf.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F10-things-only-augusta-national-members-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELegend%20has%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20years%20ago%2C%20Bill%20Gates%20didn't%20reserve%20a%20club%20room%20ahead%20of%20the%20Jamboree%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Augusta%20National's%20members-only%20tournament%20that%20occurs%20a%20few%20weeks%20before%20the%20Masters.%20The%20tech%20mogul%20had%20to%20slum%20it%20at%20a%20local%20Red%20Roof%20Inn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20one%20thing%20billionaires%20%E2%80%94%20and%20regular%20Masters%20goers%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0can%20save%20money%20is%20on%20food.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-concessions-prices-cheap-pimento-cheese-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_b