3BIn%20our%20school%20cafeterias%20and%20food%20preparation%20centers%2C%20we%20play%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20the%20educational%20process%20by%20providing%20nutritious%20meals%20for%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20California%20School%20Employees%20Association%20says%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcsea.com%2Fabout-csea%2Four-story%2Fessential-workers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BFor%20many%20students%2C%20the%20meal%20they%20receive%20at%20school%20is%20the%20best%20or%20only%20meal%20they%20will%20get%20each%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20school%20districts%20are%20boosting%20pay%20to%20attract%20more%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20Sacramento%20City%20Unified%20School%20District%20reached%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scusd.edu%2Fpress-release%2Fjoint-statement-scusd-and-seiu-regarding-compensation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagreement%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%20with%20Service%20Employees%20International%20Union%20Local%201021%20to%20boost%20pay%20to%20at%20least%20%2420%20an%20hour%20from%20July%201.%20As%20well%20as%20food-service%20workers%2C%20the%20new%20wages%20cover%20workers%20in%20other%20low-paying%20roles%20like%20custodians%2C%20bus%20drivers%2C%20and%20instructional%20aides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasing%20pay%20isn't%20an%20option%20for%20all%20school%20districts%20though.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20don't%20have%20the%20increase%20in%20revenue%20to%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20additional%20funding%20for%20staff%2C%26quot%3B%20Gretchen%20Janson%2C%20the%20assistant%20superintendent%20of%20business%20services%20at%20the%20Lynwood%20Unified%20School%20District%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20County%2C%20told%20the%20AP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20district's%20food-service%20workers%20had%20a%20starting%20salary%20of%20%2417.70%20an%20hour%2C%20which%20maxed%20out%20at%20%2421.51%2C%20and%20that%20they're%20not%20eligible%20for%20health%20benefits%20because%20the%20district's%20food-service%20staff%20only%20work%20three%20hours%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20difficult%20when%20large%20companies%20like%20McDonald's%20offer%20a%20lot%20more%20money%20per%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20unidentified%20school%20food%20service%20director%20in%20California%20said%20in%20a%20survey%20included%20in%20the%20California%20School%20Nutrition%20Association%20and%20Chef%20Ann%20Foundation%20report.%20%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20afford%20to%20pay%20at%20those%20rates.%20Thus%2C%20it%20makes%20getting%20qualified%20and%20reliable%20staff%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.schooljobs.com%2Fcareers%2Flongbeachusd%2Fjobs%2F4460877%2Fnutrition-services-worker%3Fpage%3D2%26pagetype%3DjobOpportunitiesJobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evacancies%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20nutrition%20services%20worker%20roles%20at%20the%20Long%20Beach%20Unified%20School%20District%20list%20their%20pay%20as%20between%20%2417.09%20and%20%2421.18%20an%20hour%2C%20with%20staff%20generally%20working%20between%20two%20and%20three%20hours%20a%20week.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edjoin.org%2FHome%2FJobPosting%2F1918411%3Futm_source%3Dziprecruiter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnother%20vacancy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20a%20food-services%20worker%20role%20in%20Riverside%20County%2C%20is%20for%2036%20hours%20a%20week%20at%20between%20%2418.30%20and%20%2419.42%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20pay%20aside%2C%20jobs%20at%20school%20districts%20have%20some%20benefits%20that%20make%20them%20attractive%20compared%20to%20working%20in%20fast%20food%2C%20the%20AP%20reported.%20These%20include%20health%20insurance%2C%20paid%20vacations%2C%20pensions%2C%20and%20regular%20shifts%20that%20don't%20include%20night%20or%20weekend%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Foes%2Fcurrent%2Fnaics4_611100.htm%2335-0000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%