li%3EHere%20are%20the%20requirements.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EItaly%20is%20welcoming%20globetrotting%20professionals%20with%20open%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomad-virtual-assistant-job-countries-mexico-home-base-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20nomad%3C%2Fa%3E%20visa%20went%20into%20effect%20last%20week%20after%20being%20discussed%20by%20Italian%20legislators%20for%20years%2C%20and%20it's%20aimed%20at%20remote%20workers%20who%20want%20to%20spend%20some%20time%20living%20in%20the%20popular%20European%20destination%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.euronews.com%2Ftravel%2F2024%2F04%2F08%2Fitalys-digital-nomad-visa-when-it-will-be-available-and-who-can-get-it-according-to-an-exp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEuronews%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Italian%20government%20defines%20digital%20nomads%20as%20non-European%20Union%20or%20Swiss%20citizens%20who%20are%20highly%20skilled%2C%20Euronews%20said.%20They%20should%20be%20able%20to%20work%20remotely%2C%20either%20as%20someone%20self-employed%20or%20in%20collaboration%20with%20or%20as%20an%20employee%20of%20a%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20as%20simple%20as%20showing%20up%20with%20your%20luggage%20and%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisa%20applicants%20must%20earn%20three%20times%20the%20minimum%20level%20required%20for%20exemption%20from%20participation%20in%20healthcare%20costs.%20That%20comes%20out%20to%20just%20under%20%E2%82%AC28%2C000%20annually%20or%20about%20%2430%2C400.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%20requirements%20include%20health%20insurance%20coverage%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20your%20stay%2C%20proof%20of%20accommodation%2C%20and%20candidates%20will%20have%20to%20show%20they've%20been%20a%20remote%20worker%20elsewhere%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months%20or%20a%20digital%20nomad%20for%20the%20same%20period%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20digit