%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20CEO%20Colonel%20Vinod%20Bisht%20gave%20an%20update%20on%20pacer%20Mayank%20Yadav's%20injury.%20During%20LSG's%20win%20over%20Gujarat%20Titans%2C%20Mayank's%20bowling%20was%20much-anticipated%20by%20fans%2C%20who%20were%20impressed%20with%20the%20bowler's%20pace%2C%20line%20and%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20hitting%20150%20kmph%20consistently.%20But%20in%20the%20GT%20clash%2C%20Mayank%20looked%20a%20little%20off%2C%20barely%20able%20to%20touch%20140%20kmph%20and%20was%20hit%20for%20three%20boundaries.%20After%20delivering%20his%20only%20over%2C%20Mayank%20walked%20off%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMayank%20felt%20soreness%20in%20the%20lower%20abdominal%20area%20and%20as%20a%20precaution%2C%20we%20are%20managing%20his%20workload%20over%20the%20next%20week.%20We%20hope%20to%20see%20him%20soon%20in%20the%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinod%20Bisht%20said%20in%20an%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20just%20two%20to%20three%20matches%2C%20Mayank%20has%20gathered%20headlines%20for%20his%20sheer%20pace%2C%20touching%20bowling%20speeds%20of%20150%20kmph-plus%20consistently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20match%20against%20RCB%2C%20Yadav%20bagged%20three%20wickets%20in%20his%20four-over%20spell%2C%20giving%20only%2014%20runs.%20Following%20his%20remarkable%20spell%2C%20the%20pacer%20was%20named%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LSG%20seamer%20scripted%20history%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021%20as%20he%20became%20the%20first%20bowler%20in%20the%20history%20of%20IPL%20to%20win%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award%20in%20their%20first%20two%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20clocked%20156.7%20kph%20during%20the%20game%20against%20RCB%20and%20bowled%20the%20fastest%20delivery%20in%20the%20ongoing%20edition%20and%20overall%20the%20fourth%20fastest%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20entire%20tournament%2C%20breaking%20his%20own%20record%20made%20during%20the%20Punjab%20Kings%20match%20which%20was%20his%20debut%2C%20where%20he%20clocked%20155.8%20kmph.%20During%20his%20debut%20game%2C%20he%20took%203%2F27%20in%20four%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20Mayank's%20pace%20that%20has%20many%20terming%20him%20as%20the%20next%20big%20Indian%20pace%20prospect%2C%20it%20is%20also%20the%20control%20over%20his%20line%20and%20length%20and%20intimidation%20that%20he%20has%20produced%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20matches%20that%20stands%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20consecutive%20three-wicket%20hauls%20in%20his%20first%20two%20games%20also%20helped%20him%20enter%20the%20elite%20list%20of%20players.%20Yadav%20became%20the%20sixth%20bowler%20to%20scalp%20three-plus%20wicket%20hauls%20in%20each%20of%20their%20first%20two%20IPL%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2021-year-old%20pacer%20now%20has%20joined%20the%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Lasith%20Malinga%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F639-lasith-malinga-playerprofile%5C%22%3ELasith%20Malinga%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Amit%20Singh%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mayank%20Markande%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108589-mayank-markande-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMayank%20Markande%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jofra%20Archer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64664-jofra-archer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJofra%20Archer%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20ANI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712739780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4qh589mo_mayank-yadav-afp_625x300_03_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Findias-156-7-kmph-sensation-mayank-yadav-for-t20-world-cup-report-notes-4-concerns-5405908%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mayank%20Yadav%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20revelation%20in%20the%20ongoing%20IPL%202024%20and%2