rt%20will%20reopen%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20raised%20the%20matter%20before%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20this%20morning%20and%20sought%20an%20urgent%20hearing.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20refused%20to%20specify%20if%20a%20hearing%20will%20be%20granted%20today.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20see%2C%20we%20will%20look%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20yesterday%20dismissed%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20challenge%20to%20his%20March%2021%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%20The%20court%20held%20that%20the%20central%20agency%20was%20left%20with%20%26quot%3Blittle%20option%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20AAP%20leader%20skipped%20multiple%20summonses%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case.%20It%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20ED's%20allegation%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20use%20and%20concealment%20of%20alleged%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20stressed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20separate%20protocol%20for%20a%20probe%20agency%20to%20follow%20for%20questioning%20a%20common%20man%20and%20a%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20this%20Court%20holds%20that%20this%20Court%20would%20not%20lay%20down%20two%20different%20categories%20of%20laws%2C%20one%20for%20common%20citizens%2C%20and%20the%20other%20granting%20special%20privilege%20to%20be%20extended%20by%20investigating%20agency%20to%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20or%20any%20other%20person%20in%20power%20only%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20being%20in%20that%20public%20office%20since%20that%20public%20office%20is%20enjoyed%20by%20that%20public%20figure%20due%20to%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said%20in%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20has%20said%20they%20are%20hopeful%20of%20a%20favourable%20verdict%20in%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%20said%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI%20did%20not%20find%20even%20a%20rupee%20during%20their%20searches%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20talking%20about%20crores.%20But%20ED%20and%20CBI%20have%20not%20found%20even%20a%20rupee%20of%20illegal%20money.%20Witnesses%20have%20been%20pressured%20to%20change%20their%20statements%20and%20say%20what%20ED%20wants%20them%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20issue%20is%20not%20about%20money%20laundering.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20political%20conspiracy%20in%20India's%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712738160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1o4sf5l8_arvind-kejriwal-ani_625x300_24_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-setback-for-arvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-wont-hear-his-appeal-today-5411877%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20will%20be%20spending%20this%20weekend%20in%20Tihar%20jail%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20not%20hearing%20today%20his%20challenge%20to%20yesterday's%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20ruling%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-setback-for-arvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-wont-hear-his-appeal-today-5411877%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-setback-for-arvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-wont-hear-his-appeal-today-5411877%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-setback-for-arvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-wont-hear-his-appeal-today-5411877%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Eid%20prayers%20held%20next%20to%20destroyed%20Gaza%20mosque%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe