7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Do%20India%20Really%20Need%20Virat%20Kohli%20For%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%3F%20Here's%20An%20Answer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20begins%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%202024%20concludes%2C%20and%20it%20provides%20another%20opportunity%20for%20India%20to%20end%20their%20ICC%20trophy%20drought.%20Plenty%20of%20players%20will%20be%20hoping%20to%20make%20the%20cut%20for%20India's%2015-member%20squad%20for%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20West%20Indies%20and%20USA.%20With%20the%20ongoing%20IPL%20season%20seen%20as%20auditions%20for%20the%20marquee%20ICC%20event%2C%20India's%20think%20tank%20will%20be%20carefully%20analysing%20player%20performances%20with%20some%20spots%20in%20the%20squad%20still%20up%20for%20grabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20batting%20though%20will%20still%20revolve%20around%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20who%20is%20wearing%20the%20Orange%20Cap%20after%20smashing%20316%20runs%20in%20five%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%20105.33%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20146.30%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20right-hander%20has%20hit%20three%2050-plus%20scores%20in%20IPL%202024%2C%20including%20the%20highest%20score%20of%20an%20unbeaten%20113%20for%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20against%20Rajasthan%20Royals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpening%20the%20batting%20for%20RCB%20this%20season%2C%20Kohli's%20strike%20rate%20has%20been%20significantly%20higher%20than%20his%20overall%20IPL%20strike%20rate%20of%20130.63.%20However%2C%20it%20it%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20Kohli%20will%20be%20utilised%20by%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20has%20donned%20the%20role%20of%20aggressor%20as%20an%20opener%20for%20RCB%20this%20season%2C%20Kohli%20has%20also%20shown%20that%20he's%20still%20capable%20of%20anchoring%20an%20innings%20if%20the%20situation%20demands%20him%20to.%20His%20unbeaten%20113%20against%20Rajasthan%20and%2083%20not%20out%20against%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20are%20a%20testament%20to%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20let's%20take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20type%20of%20role%20Kohli%20can%20be%20tasked%20to%20undertake%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKohli%20in%20T20%20World%20Cups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20India%20skipper%20has%20been%20a%20true%20match-winner%20for%20India%20since%20his%20international%20debut.%20In%20T20%20World%20Cups%2C%20he%20has%20scored%201%2C141%20runs%20in%2025%20innings%20at%20an%20outstanding%20average%20of%2081.50%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20over%20130.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20his%20astonishing%20numbers%2C%20he%20was%20named%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Tournament%20consecutively%20in%20the%202014%20and%202016%20editions%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20match-winning%20knocks%20in%20crucial%20outings%20-%2072*%20vs%20South%20Africa%20(2014)%2C%2082*%20vs%20Australia%20(2016)%2C%20and%20the%20iconic%2082*%20vs%20Pakistan%20(2022)%20-%20are%20unmatched%20and%20remains%20special%20for%20Indian%20fans.%20Interestingly%2C%20all%20these%20knocks%20came%20with%20Kohli%20holding%20up%20one%20end%2C%20while%20wickets%20fell%20at%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20do%20the%20pitches%20in%20the%20West%20Indies%20offer%3F%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20change%20in%20soil%20composition%20and%20moisture%20levels%20has%20affected%20the%20pace%20and%20bounce%20of%20the%20pitches%20in%20the%20West%20Indies.%20These%20days%2C%20the%20venues%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20tend%20to%20be%20slow%20tracks%20which%20are%20quite%20similar%20to%20the%20ones%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20a%20few%20other%20venues%20in%20the%20subcontinent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20has%20been%20ruthless%20in%20slow%20pitches%20where%20the%20ball%20doesn't%20get%20pace%20from%20the%20pitch%20which%20makes%20him%20a%20dangerman%20to%20any%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKohli's%20T20I%20record%20in%20West%20Indies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInnings%20played%3A%203%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuns%20scored%20112%3Cbr%3E%5CnAverage%3A%2037.33%3Cbr%3E%5CnStrike%20rate%3A%20141.77%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20T20I%20numbers%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Bangladesh%20are%20also%20exceptional%2C%20where%20he%20averages%2055.83%20and%2094.40%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20%26quot%3BAnchor%26quot%3B%20Kohli%20fit%20into%20India's%20T20%20schemes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Kohli%20has%20scored%204%2C037%20runs%20in%20117%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2051.75%20and%20he%20is%20India's%20highest%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20format.%20He%20has%20smashed%2037%20fifties%20along%20with%20a%20jaw-dropping%20122*%20against%20Afghanistan%20in%20Asia%20Cup%202022.%20His%20strike%20rate%20of%20138.15%20may%20have%20room%20for%20improvement%2C%20but%20he's%20already%20shown%20that%20he%20can%20go%20hard%20at%20bowlers%20from%20the%20start%20should%20he%20deem%20it%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20India%20played%2020%20T20Is%20apart%20from%20the%20three%20Asian%20Games%20matches%20in%20China.%20Kohli%20didn't%20feature%20in%20any%20of%20them%20and%20batters%20like%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%2C%20Tilak%20Varma%2C%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20were%20given%20the%20nod%20over%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%20spell%20on%20the%20sidelines%20following%20the%20T20%20WC%202022%2C%20Kohli%20played%20his%20first%20T20%20international%20match%20in%20February%202024%20against%20Afghanistan.%20He%20scored%20only%2029%20runs%20in%20the%20two-match%20series%20but%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20170.58.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20one%20must%20also%20note%20that%20Kohli's%20recent%2067-ball%20century%20against%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20in%20IPL%202024%20was%20the%20slowest%20ton%20in%20the%20league's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20that%20the%20T20%20dynamics%20have%20changed%20drastically%20over%20the%20years%2C%20batters%20have%20become%20more%20aggressive%20from%20the%20outset%20these%20days.%20IPL%202024%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20has%20witnessed%20two%20record-breaking%20team%20scores%20this%20year%20-%20SRH's%20277%20vs%20MI%20and%20KKR's%20272%20vs%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20since%20the%20pitches%20in%20West%20Indies%20might%20not%20make%20it%20possible%20for%20many%20high-scoring%20games%20to%20take%20place%2C%20Kohli's%20presence%20in%20India's%20squad%20for%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20choice.%20His%20presence%20in%20the%20middle%20order%20as%20an%20anchor%20will%20provide%20balance%20alongside%20the%20swashbuckling%20and%20aggressive%20styles%20of%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%2C%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20and%20Shivam%20Dube.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20given%20the%20world%20many%20great%20cricketers%20but%20Virat%20Kohli%20finds%20himself%20in%20a%20league%20of%20his%20own%20in%20the%20modern%20era.%20With%20opening%20batting%20candidates%20like%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20all%20in%20the%20fray%20for%20a%20T20%20World%20Cup%20spot%2C%20making%20Kohli%20the%20anchor%20of%20the%20team%20makes%20perfect%20sense%20given%20his%20ability%20to%20play%20according%20to%20match%20situations%20as%20well%20as%20his%20extensive%20experience%20in%20the%20high%20stakes%20pressure%20situations%20which%20are%20synonymous%20with%20ICC%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712737380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F3l0h0uho_virat-kohli-bcci_625x300_10_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdoes-virat-kohli-fit-into-india-s-schemes-for-t20-world-cup-2024-5401292%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%204%2C037%20T20I%20runs%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20India's%20highest%20run-scorer%20in%20cricket's%20shortest%20format.%22%2C%22a