2title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Refuses%20To%20Accept%20Patanjali's%20Ramdev's%20Apology%2C%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20refused%20to%20accept%20an%20%26quot%3Bunconditional%20apology%26quot%3B%20of%20Patanjali%20Ayurved's%20co-founder%20Ramdev%20for%20not%20abiding%20by%20the%20undertaking%20given%20to%20it%20in%20the%20misleading%20advertisements%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoga%20guru%20Ramdev%20and%20Patanjali%20Ayurved's%20Managing%20Director%20Balkrishna%20had%20yesterday%20submitted%20an%20untendered%20apology%20to%20the%20top%20court%20and%20had%20sought%20pardon%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20apology%20is%20on%20paper.%20Their%20back%20is%20against%20the%20wall.%20We%20decline%20to%20accept%20this%2C%20we%20consider%20it%20a%20deliberate%20violation%20of%20undertaking%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20A%20Amanullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20for%20repeatedly%20violating%20its%20orders%20and%20filing%20improper%20affidavits.%C2%A0%C2%A0%26quot%3BTendering%20apology%20is%20not%20enough.%20You%20should%20suffer%20the%20consequences%20for%20violating%20the%20court's%20order.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20generous%20in%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20noted%20that%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20sent%20their%20apologies%20to%20the%20media%20first.%20%26quot%3BTill%20the%20matter%20hit%20the%20court%2C%20the%20condemners%20did%20not%20find%20it%20fit%20to%20send%20us%20the%20affidavits.%20They%20sent%20it%20to%20the%20media%20first%2C%20till%207.30%20pm%20yesterday%20it%20was%20not%20uploaded%20for%20us.%20They%20believe%20in%20publicity%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kohli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20on%20April%202%20too%20had%20refused%20to%20accept%20an%20apology%20tendered%20by%20Patanjali%20after%20the%20top%20court%20rap%20during%20the%20earlier%20hearing.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20happy%20with%20your%20apology%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20them%20a%20last%20opportunity%20to%20file%20affidavits%20within%20a%20week%2C%20the%20bench%20took%20strong%20note%20of%20their%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20defiance%26quot%3B%20in%20not%20following%20the%20undertaking%20given%20before%20it%20in%20the%20case%20filed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20undertaking%20given%20to%20court%20and%20you%20have%20broken%20every%20barrier%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20have%20made%20sure%20that%20the%20solemn%20undertaking%20should%20have%20been%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit.%20We%20can%20also%20say%20that%20we%20are%20sorry%20for%20not%20accepting%20it.%20Your%20apology%20is%20not%20persuading%20this%20court.%20It%20is%20more%20of%20a%20lip%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20February%2027%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20directed%20the%20company%20to%20stop%20all%20electronic%20and%20print%20advertisements%20of%20its%20medicines%20giving%20misleading%26quot%3B%20information%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20began%20in%20November%20last%20year%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%2C%20cautioned%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20against%20making%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20claims%20in%20advertisements%20about%20its%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIMA%20had%20referred%20to%20several%20advertisements%20which%20allegedly%20projected%20the%20allopathy%20and%20the%20doctors%20in%20poor%20light%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bdisparaging%26quot%3B%20statements%20have%20also%20been%20made%20by%20firms%2C%20engaged%20in%20the%20production%20of%20ayurvedic%20medicines%2C%20to%20mislead%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20commercials%20say%20that%20the%20medical%20practitioners%20themselves%20are%20dying%20despite%20taking%20modern%20medicines%2C%20the%20counsel%20for%20the%20IMA%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712736540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fimg11vg8_ramdev_625x300_27_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-accept-patanjalis-ramdevs-apology-again-5411591%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20refused%20to%20accept%20an%20%26quot%3Bunconditional%20apology%26quot%3B%20of%20Patanjali%20Ayurved's%20co-founder%20Ramdev%20for%20not%20abiding%20by%20the%20undertaking%20given%20to%20it%20in%20the%20misleading%20advertisements%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-accept-patanjalis-ramdevs-apology-again-5411591%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-accept-patanjalis-ramdevs-apology-again-5411591%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-accept-patanjalis-ramdevs-apology-again-5411591%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Louis%20Tomlinson%20addresses%20'Larry'%20conspiracy%20theories%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712736511000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109188762%2Cimgsize-50706.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Flouis-tomlinson-addresses-larry-conspiracy-theories-about-relationship-with-harry-styles%2Farticleshow%2F109188823.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C