Breaking%20Into%20200%20Homes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20US%20woman%2C%20who%20describes%20herself%20as%20as%20a%20former%20%26quot%3Bcat%20burglar''%20has%20opened%20up%20about%20how%20she%20broke%20into%20more%20than%20200%20homes%20and%C2%A0stole%20over%20%247%20million%20(Rs%C2%A058%2C22%2C71%2C550).%C2%A0Jennifer%20Gomez%20recently%20appeared%20on%20''Locked%20In%20with%20Ian%20Bick''%20and%20revealed%20her%20methods%20and%20tactics%2C%20listing%20what%20she%20would%20look%20for%20in%20a%20home%20that%20she%20was%20going%20to%20burglarize%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F04%2F09%2Freal-estate%2Fex-cat-burglar-shares-how-she-broke-into-200-homes-stole-7m%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20As%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20''cat%20burglars''%20are%20essentially%20thieves%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20are%20adept%20at%20entering%20and%20leaving%20the%20burglarized%20place%20without%20attracting%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGomez%2C%20who%20was%20in%20prison%20between%202011%20and%202020%20for%20burglary%2C%20mostly%20targeted%C2%A0affluent%20neighbourhoods%20in%20Florida.%C2%A0''I%20always%20wanted%20nice%20homes.%20I%20mean%2C%20at%20least%20million-dollar%20homes.%20I%20would%20always%20try%20to%20find%20a%20home%20that%20was%20in%20a%20cul-de-sac%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20get%20lost%20in%20there%20%E2%80%A6%20or%20a%20home%20that%20backed%20up%20to%20a%20street%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gomez%20confessed%20during%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20thief%20further%20said%20that%20her%20intimate%20knowledge%20of%20wealthy%20lifestyles%20helped%20her%20craft%20her%20criminal%20exploits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20knew%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20about%20how%20wealthy%20people%20lived%20because%20my%20parents%20were%20both%20physicians.%20They're%20probably%20going%20to%20have%20a%20privacy%20fence%20of%20some%20kind.%20I%20can%20hide%20behind%20that%20when%20I%20get%20in%20their%20backyard.%20I'm%20completely%20concealed%2C''%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20she%20carefully%20curated%20her%20wardrobe%2C%20studied%C2%A0pet%20behaviour%2C%20deciphered%20security%20setup%20clues%2C%20and%20owned%20sophisticated%20tools%20to%20gain%20easy%20entry%20into%20houses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20prison%2C%C2%A0Gomez%2C%20now%20a%20TikTok%20Influencer%2C%20advises%20others%20on%20how%20to%20keep%20their%20homes%20safe%20from%20burglaries%C2%A0by%20pointing%20out%20things%20she%20used%20to%20look%20out%20for%20to%20see%20whether%20a%20house%20would%20be%20profitable%20to%20target.%C2%A0''There's%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20you%20can%20tell%20from%20the%20outside%20of%20a%20home%20that%20will%20give%20a%20burglar%20a%20lot%20of%20information.%20Stop%20advertising%20everything%20that's%20going%20on%20in%20your%20house%20and%20with%20your%20house%2C''%20she%20urged%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FmJcOUeOBpZQ%3Fsi%3DAbaUFdngx5-Me0Dr%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Delve%20into%20Jennifer%20Gomez's%20fascinating%20journey%20from%20ordinary%20life%20to%20sophisticated%20cat%20burglar%2C%20breaking%20into%20nearly%20200%20homes%20and%20accumulating%20over%20%247%20million.%20Uncover%20her%20ingenious%20tricks%2C%20eventual%20capture%2C%20and%20the%20unique%20challenges%20of%20giving%20birth%20while%20serving%20a%2010-year%20prison%20sentence%2C''%20the%20video%20was%20captioned%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712736120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F9pklgrn_jennifer-gomez_625x300_10_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A