tes%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20Patanjali%20case%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20authorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Uttarakhand%20licensing%20authority%C2%A0was%20merely%20pushing%20files%20and%20did%20nothing.%20The%20state%20authorities%20are%20hand%20in%20glove%20with%20the%20contemnors.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20are%20dealing%20with%20people's%20lives%C2%A0and%20you%20have%20been%20playing%20with%20people's%20lives.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20did%20you%20do%20when%20people%20were%20having%20these%20medicines%20and%20were%20being%20fooled%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20four-five%20years%2C%20State%20Licensing%20Authority%20remained%20in%20deep%20slumber...you%20are%20acting%20like%20a%20post%20office%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhy%20should%20we%20not%20think%20you%20are%20in%20cahoots%20with%20the%20alleged%20contemnors%3F%20You%20are%20keeping%20your%20eyes%20shut%20deliberately.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20have%20strong%20objection%20to%20the%20use%20of%20the%20word%20'bonafide'%20for%20officers.%20We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20take%20lightly.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Framdev-supreme-court-patanjali-we-are-not-blind-supreme-court-raps-ramdev-again-rejects-apology-5411262%5C%22%3EWe%20will%20rip%20you%20apart%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20Patanjali%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20apology%20is%20not%20worth%20the%20paper%20it%20is%20written%20on.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETendering%20apology%20is%20not%20enough.%20You%20should%20suffer%20the%20consequences%20for%20violating%20the%20court's%20order.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20generous%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne%20man%20seeks%20mercy%2C%20what%20about%20those%20countless%20innocent%20people%20who%20took%20the%20medicine%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPatanjali%20MD%20and%20Ramdev%20tried%20to%20evade%20personal%20appearance%20before%20the%20court%20by%20making%20false%20claims%20of%20travel%20abroad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712736060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fc1l320oo_supreme-court-ani_625x300_23_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fapology-not-worth-the-paper-written-on-supreme-court-in-patanjali-case-5411522%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20rejected%20the%20latest%20apology%20filed%20by%20Patanjali%20founders%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20for%20its%20misleading%20ads%20and%20rebuked%20the%20state%20authorities%20for%20being%20in%20%26quot%3Bhand%20in%20gloves%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fapology-not-worth-the-paper-written-on-supreme-court-in-patanjali-case-5411522%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fapology-not-worth-the-paper-written-on-supreme-court-in-patanjali-case-5411522%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fapology-not-worth-the-paper-written-on-supreme-court-in-patanjali-case-5411522%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Will%20Rip%20You%20Apart%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20To%20Authorities%20In%20Patanjali%20Ads%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERejecting%20another%20set%20of%20apologies%20filed%20by%20Patanjali%20founders%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20for%20the%20company's%20misleading%20ads%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20not%20blind%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20generous%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20case.%20The%20court%20tore%20into%20the%20Uttarakhand%20licensing%20authority%20for%20not%20acting%20against%20Patanjali%20for%20so%20long%2C%20and%20also%C2%A0noted%20that%20it%20is%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20Centre's%20reply%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20apology%20is%20on%20paper.%20Their%20back%20is%20against%20the%20wall.%20We%20decline%20to%20accept%20this%2C%20we%20consider%20it%20a%20deliberate%20violation%20of%20undertaking%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Justice%20A%20Amanullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20proceedings%2C%20the%20bench%20noted%20that%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20sent%20their%20apologies%20to%20the%20media%20first.%20%26quot%3BTill%20the%20matter%20hit%20the%20court%2C%20the%20contemnors%20did%20not%20find%20it%20fit%20to%20send%20us%20the%20affidavits.%20They%20sent%20it%20to%20the%20media%20first%2C%20till%207.30%20pm%20yesterday%20it%20was%20not%20uploaded%20for%20us.%20They%20believe%20in%20publicity%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kohli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Patanjali%20founders%2C%20said%20he%20cannot%20speak%20for%20the%20registry%20and%20that%20the%20apologies%20had%20been%20served.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20read%20out%20the%20affidavits%2C%20Justice%20Amanullah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20defrauding%20the%20affidavit.%20Who%20drafted%20it%2C%20I%20am%20surprised.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rohatgi%20said%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Blapse%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20which%20the%20court%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3Bvery%20small%20word%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Amanullah%20asked%20if%20the%20apology%20is%20%26quot%3Beven%20heartfelt%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20else%20needs%20to%20be%20said%2C%20my%20lords%2C%20we%20will.%20He%20is%20not%20(a)%20professional%20litigant.%20People%20make%20mistakes%20in%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rohatgi%20replied.%20%26quot%3BEven%20after%20our%20orders%3F%20Tendering%20apology%20is%20not%20enough.%20You%20should%20suffer%20the%20consequences%20for%20violating%20the%20court's%20order.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20generous%20in%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20a%20message%20needs%20to%20go%20out%20to%20the%20society%20at%20large.%20%26quot%3B(This%20is)%20not%20just%20about%20one%20FMCG%20but%20violation%20of%20the%20law.%20Look%20at%20your%20replies%20to%20state%20authority%20when%20they%20asked%20you%20to%20withdraw%2C%20you%20said%20HC%20said%20no%20coercive%20steps%20against%20us.%20We%20are%20making%20it%20a%20part%20of%20your%20conduct%2C%20(the)%20larger%20picture%20is%20your%20conduct%20with%20the%20public%20at%20large%20but%20saying%20it%20is%20in%20good%20faith.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20turned%20to%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20and%20questioned%20why%20licensing%20inspectors%20did%20not%20act%20and%20that%20three%20officers%20should%20be%20suspended%20at%20once.%C2%A0The%20court%20said%20the%20state's%20officers%20had%20done%20nothing.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20strong%20objection%20to%20the%20use%20of%20the%20word%20'bonafide'%20for%20officers.%20We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20take%20(it)%20lightly.%20We%20will%20rip%20you%20apart%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20saying%20that%20officers%20were%20just%20%26quot%3Bpushing%20files%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202021%2C%20the%20ministry%20wrote%20to%20the%20Uttarakhand%20licensing%20authority%20against%20a%20misleading%20advertisement.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20company%20gave%20a%20response%20to%20the%20licensing%20authority.%20However%2C%20the%20authority%20let%20off%20the%20company%20with%20a%20warning.%20The%201954%20Act%20does%20not%20provide%20for%20warning%20and%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20for%20compounding%20the%20offence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20happened%20six%20times%2C%20back%20and%20forth%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20the%20licensing%20inspector%20remained%20quiet.%20There%20is%20no%20report%20by%20the%20officer.%20The%20person%20appointed%20subsequently%20acted%20the%20same%20way.%20All%20those%20three%20officers%20should%20be%20suspended%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20licensing%20authority%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20cahoots%20with%20the%20contemnors%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20being%20mocked.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20acting%20like%20a%20post%20office.%20Did%20you%20take%20legal%20advice%3F%20Shameful%20of%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20told%20the%20state%20counsel.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20we%20agree%20that%20you%20are%20hand-in-glove%20with%20Patanjali%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked%20the%20authority%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20have%20being%20playing%20with%20people's%20life%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Uttarakhand%20counsel%20told%20the%20court%20that%20they%20will%20take%20action%2C%20Justice%20Kohli%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BThank%20God%2C%20now%20you%20have%20woken%20up%20at%20last%20and%20realise%20that%20there%20is%20a%20statute%20existing.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20all%20the%20faceless%20people%20who%20have%20consumed%20these%20Patanjali%20medicines%20stated%20to%20cure%20diseases%20which%20cannot%20be%20cured.%20Can%20you%20do%20this%20to%20an%20ordinary%20person%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%C2%A0The%20licensing%20authority%20apologised%20to%20the%20court%20and%20assured%20that%20they%20will%20surely%20act%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20then%20said%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20tried%20to%20wriggle%20out%20of%20physical%20appearance%20in%20court%20and%20said%20they%20were%20travelling%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20licensing%20authority%2C%20it%20noted%2C%20was%20in%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20slumber%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisdain%26quot%3B%20shown%20by%20Divya%20pharmacy%20to%20the%20warnings%20of%20state%20authority%20is%20%26quot%3Bapparent%20from%20tone%20and%20tenor%20of%20the%20reply%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20all%20who%20held%20post%20as%20district%20ayurvedic%20and%20unani%20officers%20who%20held%20posts%20from%202018%20till%20now%20shall%20file%20replies%20on%20actions%20taken%20by%20them%20against%20these%20ads.%20The%20court%20said%20it%20will%20pass%20orders%20on%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20on%20April%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712736000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcsgndupo_ramdev-ani-_625x300_10_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Framdev-supreme-court-patanjali-we-are-not-blind-supreme-court-raps-ramdev-again-rejects-apology-5411262%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rejecting%20apologies%20filed%20by%20Patanjali%20founders%20Ramdev%20and%20Balkrishna%20for%20the%20company's%20misleading%20ads%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20not%20blind%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20generous%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20case%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A70%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Framdev-supreme-court-patanjali-we-are-not-blind-supreme-court-raps-ramdev-again-rejects-apology-5411262%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Framdev-supreme-court-patanjali-we-are-not-blind-supreme-court-raps-ramdev-again-rejects-apology-5411262%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Framdev-supreme-court-patanjali-we-are-not-blind-supreme-court-raps-ramdev-again-rejects-apology-5411262%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20stock%20market%20closed%20for%20Eid%3F%20BSE%2C%20NSE%20holidays%20in%20April%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712735683000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109188157%2Cimgsize-86472.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fis-the-stock-market-closed-for-eid-ul-fitr-bse-nse