ner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345758%2Fbest-places-for-ramzan-food-in-bengaluru-iftar-ramadan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eiftar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20fast-breaking%20evening%20meal)%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20signal%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20fast.%20Hours%20of%20abstaining%20from%20food%20and%20drink%20would%20make%20my%20friends%20hungry%20enough%20to%20devour%20everything%20in%20front%20of%20them%2C%20I%20would%20think.%20But%20I%E2%80%99d%20watch%20in%20awe%20as%20they%20elegantly%20took%20some%20%3Cem%3Ekhajoor%3C%2Fem%3E%20(dates)%2C%20followed%20by%20fresh%20fruits%20and%20then%20meaty%20snacks%2C%20and%20the%20likes.%20The%20%3Cem%3Eiftar%3C%2Fem%3E%20would%20then%20be%20washed%20down%20with%20a%20drink%20of%20%3Cem%3Eroohafza%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20refreshing%20drink%20made%20with%20basil%20seeds%2C%20fruits%2C%20herbs%20and%20flowers).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20among%20many%20other%20delicacies%20set%20before%20us%2C%20one%20dish%20reigned%20supreme%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eseviyan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20vermicelli%20pudding%20made%20with%20ghee%2C%20rice%20vermicelli%20noodles%2C%20milk%2C%20spices%2C%20and%20a%20sweetener.%20While%20it%20is%20a%20common%20guest%20at%20the%3Cem%3E%20iftar%3C%2Fem%3E%20feast%2C%20my%20friend%20Thousif%20Raza%20explains%20it%20is%20its%20fancier%20cousin%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esheer%20khurma%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20makes%20an%20appearance%20on%20Eid.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESheer%20khurma%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20made%20with%20extra%20%3Cem%3Ekhoya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(thickened%20milk)%20and%20dry%20fruits%20%E2%80%94%20a%20richer%20version%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eseviyan%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20nevertheless%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247633%2Fla-kheer-deli-shivang-sood-pune-startup-kheer-indian-traditional-dessert-homemade-recipes-success-story-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D