india.com%2F283166%2Fuber-india-sahib-echoes-cafe-delhi-inspiring-indians%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20individuals%20with%20conditions%20like%20microtia%2C%20whose%20external%20ears%20are%20underdeveloped%3F%20Could%20this%20technology%20present%20a%20non-surgical%2C%20cost-effective%20solution%20for%20millions%20worldwide%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanishka%E2%80%99s%20mind%20buzzed%20with%20possibilities%2C%20igniting%20a%20passion%20to%20explore%20the%20untapped%20potential%20of%20this%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20resounding%20affirmation%20of%20their%20journey%2C%20Kanishka%20and%20Raj%20Shah%20have%20indeed%20forged%20a%20remarkable%20path%20over%20seven%20years.%20Through%20their%20company%20WeHear%2C%20the%20two%20have%20built%20HearNU%20%E2%80%94%20a%20hearing%20aid%20that%20uses%20bone%20conduction%20technology%2C%20offering%20a%20non-surgical%20solution%20for%20people%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss.%20They%20have%20also%20developed%20bone%20conduction%20earphones%20called%20WeHear%20OX%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20earphone%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20sit%20inside%20your%20ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeHear%20has%20a%20granted%20patent%20for%20its%20HearNU%20and%20is%20transforming%20the%20lives%20of%20thousands%20of%20young%20children%20and%20adults%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss%2C%20in%20which%20sound%20waves%20are%20not%20able%20to%20carry%20all%20the%20way%20through%20to%20the%20inner%20ear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanishka%20and%20Raj%20claim%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20only%20bone-conduction%20hearing%20aid%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20Since%20their%20launch%20in%202021%2C%20they%20have%20sold%20over%2011%2C500%20devices%20and%20have%20earned%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%205.5%20crore%20in%20FY%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20in%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203%20from%20Peyush%20Bansal%2C%20valuing%20their%20company