ing%20%E2%80%94%20victims%20of%20modernisation%20and%20the%20relentless%20march%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Neelam%20refused%20to%20let%20them%20fade%20into%20obscurity.%20He%20understood%20that%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20changing%20climate%2C%20adaptation%20was%20key%2C%20and%20these%20heirlooms%20held%20the%20secrets%20to%20survival.%20His%20endeavour%20became%20a%20symbol%20of%20resilience%2C%20a%20guardian%20of%20tradition%20in%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHeirloom%20seeds%2C%20passed%20down%20for%20at%20least%2050%20years%2C%20are%20resistant%20to%20floods.%20This%20is%20a%20vital%20trait%20in%20combating%20food%20security%20threats%20posed%20by%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20Neelam%2C%20now%2037%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20sadly%2C%20due%20to%20the%20increasing%20adoption%20of%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20in%20the%20Northeast%20are%20abandoning%20heirloom%20varieties.%20This%2C%20coupled%20with%20frequent%20floods%2C%20has%20made%20agriculture%20unsustainable%20in%20the%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forga