cal%20doctor%20by%20profession%20but%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20farm%20in%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%20But%20sadly%2C%20Neelam%E2%80%99s%20father%20passed%20away%20from%20a%20stroke%20while%20Neelam%20was%20studying%20in%20Class%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20completing%20Class%2012%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20graduation%20in%20arts%20from%20an%20open%20school.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20so%20disinterested%20that%20I%20neglected%20to%20submit%20assignments%20required%20to%20complete%20the%20degree%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20Pabhoi%20village%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Heirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346322%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHeirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20he%20inherited%2