0have%20still%20been%20preserved%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Zeenia%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sarfaraz%20points%20out%20that%20this%20consistency%20is%20what%20has%20kept%20them%20relevant%20even%20today%2C%20the%20cousins%20emphasise%20that%20the%20staff%20who%20work%20with%20them%20are%20integral%20to%20the%20success%20of%20the%20family.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CRight%20from%20the%20senior%20heads%20of%20the%20company%20to%20the%20person%20who%20sweeps%20the%20floor%2C%20everybody%20puts%20in%20absolute%20effort.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20makes%20us%20what%20we%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20fair%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20has%20been%20winning%20the%20hearts%20and%20palates%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20residents%20for%20over%20a%20century.%20And%20the%20love%20for%20this%20legendary%20business%20seems%20to%20only%20grow%20in%20leaps%20and%20bounds%20with%20every%20passing%20day%20%E2%80%94%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20legacy%20that%20Ardeshir%20wanted%20to%20leave%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712236947000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345649%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20started%20with%20founder%20Nariman%20Ardeshir%20delivering%20milk%20cans%20in%20Mumbai's%20Kalbadevi%2C%20is%20now%20a%20celebrated%20empire.%20The%20success%20of%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20is%20rooted%20in%20its%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20purity%2C%20tradition%2C%20and%20familial%20unity%20enduring%20through%20generations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345649%2Fhistory-of-parsi-dairy-farm-mumbai-nariman-ardeshir-legacy%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%2